'''''Tale of Four''''', ni filime ngufi yo muri Amerika yo muri 2017 iyobowe na Gabourey Sidibe nk'umukinnyi we wa mbere  ikanakorwa na Kia Perry, Lisa Cortes na Shannon Gibson.  filimi igenda izunguruka mubagore bane batandukanye bafite inzira enye zitandukanye aho igishekeje ubuzima bwabo bwose burahura. Ishingiye ku ndirimbo ""Four Women" yaririmbwe na nyakwigendera umuririmbyi akaba n'umurwanashyaka wa politiki Nina Simone. 

Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Ledisi Young, Meagan Kimberly Smith, Dana Gourrier na Aisha Hinds.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere muri Nzeri 2016 mu mujyi wa New York, muri New York hanyuma yerekanwa ku ya 25 Kamena 2017 mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Nantucket . Yatsindiye igihembo cya filimi ngufi nziza mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Urbanworld 2017. 

